                "invention-title": [
                    "Granular silicon production system and method",
                    "一种颗粒硅生产系统和方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides a granular silicon production system and method.The granular silicon production system comprises a cold hydrogenation device, a disproportionation reactor, a seed crystal reactor and a heterogeneous deposition reactor; an inlet of the cold hydrogenation device is used for receiving hydrogen, silicon powder and carbon tetrachloride, an outlet of the cold hydrogenation device is connected with an inlet of the disproportionation reactor, and a silane outlet of the disproportionation reactor is connected with an inlet of the seed crystal reactor and an inlet of the heterogeneous deposition reactor. A dichlorosilane outlet of the disproportionation reactor is connected with an inlet of the seed crystal reactor; a seed crystal outlet of the seed crystal reactor is connected with an inlet of the heterogeneous deposition reactor, and the inlet of the heterogeneous deposition reactor further receives hydrogen. The granular silicon seed crystal can be continuously produced on line, and secondary pollution of the seed crystal is avoided."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提供一种颗粒硅生产系统和方法，所述颗粒硅生产系统，包括冷氢化装置、歧化反应器、晶种反应器和非均相沉积反应器；所述冷氢化装置的入口用于接收氢气、硅粉和四氯化碳，冷氢化装置的出口与歧化反应器的入口连接，歧化反应器的硅烷出口与晶种反应器的入口和非均相沉积反应器的入口分别连接，歧化反应器的二氯二氢硅出口与晶种反应器的入口连接；晶种反应器的晶种出口与非均相沉积反应器的入口连接，非均相沉积反应器的入口还接收氢气。本发明能够在线连续生产颗粒硅晶种，避免晶种的二次污染。"
                }
            ]
